"""Test the tokenizer handles et al. at the end of a sentence correctly."""
text = (
    'This is in agreement with previous observations by Peng et al. It is believed that 1D growth does occur.'
    )
sents = ['This is in agreement with previous observations by Peng et al.',
    'It is believed that 1D growth does occur.']
self.assertEqual(sents, self.ps.tokenize(text))
